      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been sitting here at the edge of the cliffs in santorini for hours just watching the sun go down. it's beautiful, i guess. but i feel like i've checked every box. i've seen the ruins, i've seen the oceans, i've done the whole circuit. it feels like the itinerary is finally finished. like there's nowhere left to actually go after this.",
