      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not about being present for me. i mean, i've been \"present\" for everything, and it's just the same thing over and over. the beauty starts to feel like a performance. even the sunsets feel like they're just winding down to a close. i feel like i've reached the edge of the map and there isn't anything else on the other side, just the end of the line. it feels more like a conclusion than a journey at this point.",
