    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not about changing the mode. i mean, a cooking class? a hike? that's just more of the same scenery. it's just more noise. it's like a book that's already reached its final chapter, and you're just suggesting i go back and re-read the same pages or flip through a different chapter in a different language. the story is done. i'm just standing here at the end of the book, looking at the back cover. wouldn't it make more sense to just close it?",
